---
title: Garlic-Rosemary Steak and Herb Butter with Mushroom and Spinach Vol-au-Vents
description: Channel your inner chef with our simplified way to make this classic French puff pastry technique. Puff pastry can sense your fear, so be gentle but confident with it and the payoff will be worth it! We almost forgot to mention the tender steak topped with melty herb butter.
